107
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:34,000
dan kemudian melepaskan saya. Dan terasa sangat ganjil

108
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:37,000
bagi saya merasai apa saja jenis kesakitan,

109
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,000
