171
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:59,000
(Ketawa) Oh! Saya berasa sangat gembira.

172
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:03,000
Perasaan gembira. Ia sangat indah.

173
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,000
